# The local media you drop in for this demo is intentionally NOT committed —
# binary image/video files bloat the repo. Keep them local; the composition
# reaches them at runtime via loadAsset('./video.mp4') (preview serves them, the
# render reads them off disk). Only the source (index.ts, README) is tracked.
*.mp4
*.webm
*.mov
*.mkv
*.m4v
*.avi
*.png
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.gif
*.webp
*.avif
*.bmp
